subsection.text:

  Section 404 of the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act (
  42 U.S.C. 5170c
) is amended by adding at the end the following:


  Section 404(c)(2) of the Robert T. Stafford Disaster Relief and Emergency Assistance Act (
  42 U.S.C. 5170c(c)(2)
) is amended by inserting after applications submitted under paragraph (1). the following: Until such time as the Administrator promulgates regulations to implement this paragraph, the Administrator may waive notice and comment rulemaking, if the Administrator determines doing so is necessary to expeditiously implement this section, and may carry out this section as a pilot program..

